Title: Entropy of 2+1 dimensional de Sitter space in terms of brick wall method
Authors: Won Tae Kim
Comments: 6pages, revtex, no figures to appear in Phys. Rev. D
Report-no: SOGANG-HEP 243/98
Journal-ref: Phys.Rev. D59 (1999) 047503
\\
  We calculate the statistical entropy of a scalar field on the background of
three-dimensional De Sitter space in terms of the brick wall method and finally
derive the perimeter law of the entropy.
